column1: Hey! It's been a while!
It only feels like that because you always forget to reply to our texts.
Wait, really...? I mean, I've just got a lot of stuff to do!
I suppose it's been a little while for me too, hasn't it?
For me as well... I had no money, so I lost service.
Long time no see.
How is everyone?
It's been a long time since we last saw each other.
I'd say I'm doing well.
It's quite late though. Shouldn't you all be studying for finals?
Nah, I'm fine! Unlike Ryuji...
Stop, stop! I'm already dead!
Anyway! Here's what I really wanted to say...
Since it's almost summer vacation, why don't we get together?
Not a bad idea.
Yeah! You guys want to go on a trip?
That sounds like fun!
Perhaps Kyoto? That would be a nice place for a vacation.
No way! Kyoto trips are for high schoolers!
Sweet! We should get together somewhere and plan this out!
Where at?
Where else!?
Let's meet at the hideout.
Let's meet at our usual spot.
Roger that, Leader!
Roger that, Leader!
Heyo, got a sec? Found something interesting.
I'll let the others know! Swing by the hideout when you're free.
Good evening, [1B]S1-kun.
I'm sorry for the short notice, but could we meet up? I'd like to talk to you.

If you have time, it would make
me quite happy. I'll be waiting
in front of the fountain.
Thank you so much for helping me out with Mari-san.
I think I was able to help her because you were all there with me.
If I had been by myself, I'm sure I would have been at a loss for what to do...
I'm sorry to ask, but could I have some of your time?
I'd like to work out my feelings, but I'm worried I'll just think in circles if I'm by myself.
If you have time, that is...
I'll be waiting at Odori Park, near the fountain.
Do you have a moment, [1B]S1?
This is a bit sudden, but I must ask a favor of you.

I'll be waiting near the skewer
shop at Shinsekai. I'd greatly
appreciate it if you came.
Hey, got a sec?
Be ready to move once things settle down, okay?
I'm sure it'll all be fine. I've just got this weird feeling in my gut...
Phantom Thieves.
We have Akane Hasegawa.
If you want her back, come to Inari Taisha.
Sorry this is so sudden, but...
Could you meet me in front of Shibuya Station?
Bring everyone else too, if you can. I promise not to take too much of your time.
Well, hope to see you there.
Are you guys okay?
Hurry up and get outta there!
Dude...
I think I found someone that was in the Jail.
Can you come to the alley behind the airsoft shop?
I heard some intriguing news.
It seems there's a store on Central Street that carries clothing from Alice's brand.
Perhaps we can gain some information there?
How is the information search going?
Why don't we meet up and share what we've gathered so far?
Hey.
I might have some intel for you.
Come meet me behind the souvenir shop.
[1B]S1, there's been an emergency.
Please come to the vending machine by the pharmacy immediately.
The safest way in and out is near the crossing, where you can see the big sign.
Once you're all ready, gather there.
Roger!
We'll be exploring a new Jail... There's no telling what's waiting for us there.
Let's be sure we're ready.
We gonna head to the Jail?
If you've got a minute, stop by and see me, yeah?
I got something really cool! It's gonna blow your mind!
Yo dude!
There's somewhere I wanna go before we head out.
You should check it out too.
I'll wait for you outside, so just lemme know when you're ready!
Heyo!
Can I borrow you? There's something I wanna do before we go.
I shall await you at the entrance of the Mt. Aoba Park shrine!
Are you guys enjoying Osaka?
We're having a celebration in a bit, so don't eat too much!
Let's meet up in an hour!
Hey [1B]S1.
It's not important, but I want to talk to you about something.
Can you come see me when you have time?
My apologies for bringing this up even though we're leaving soon.
There's something I wanted to ask of you before we go.
Do you have some time to talk? Please let me know.
Hope you're resting well.
If you have some time, could you come talk to me?
I have a favor to ask... It will be easier to explain in person.
Hey, it's me.
You hungry?
Come see me. I've got some good stuff for you.
Hey! I just heard something important I wanna tell you about!
I know you're busy, but think you can stop by?
Whenever is fine, just come see me!
So, about going back to the Shibuya Jail...
I gathered some info and listed them like requests for you.
Take a look when you get to the hideout!
